## Git-Based Deployment

The server runs from a git clone of `https://github.com/JoseMoura97/ib_bot.git` on branch `portfolios-builder-allocations-ui`.

**Deploy workflow (local):**
1. Commit and push changes locally: `git push origin portfolios-builder-allocations-ui`
2. Run deploy on server via SSH:
```bash
ssh root@213.159.68.39 "cd /home/ibbot/ib_bot && GIT_TERMINAL_PROMPT=0 git pull origin portfolios-builder-allocations-ui && docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d --build"
```

Or use the deploy script on the server:
```bash
ssh root@213.159.68.39 "/home/ibbot/deploy.sh"
```

**Important:** Always commit and push ALL files the server needs (including migrations) before deploying. The server only gets what's in git. `.env` and `.cache` are gitignored and persist independently on the server.

## Common Operations

```bash
# Check status
docker compose ps

# View logs
docker compose logs -f [service]

# Restart after config change
docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d

# Rebuild after code change
docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d --build

# Force recreate (needed after .env changes)
docker compose up -d --force-recreate api worker beat

# Database access
docker compose exec db psql -U ibbot -d ibbot

# Emergency stop trading
echo "TRADING_HALT=true" >> .env && docker compose restart api worker

# Check IB Gateway status from API
docker exec ib_bot-api-1 curl -s http://localhost:8000/ib/status

# Check IB Gateway process on host
ss -tlnp | grep 4001
pgrep -fa java

# Restart socat proxy
systemctl restart ib-socat

# Start IB Gateway (manual, then login via VNC)
DISPLAY=:1 nohup /opt/ibgateway/ibgateway > /tmp/gw.log 2>&1 &

# Kill IB Gateway
pkill -f ibgateway

# Trigger plot data refresh
docker exec ib_bot-api-1 curl -s -X POST 'http://localhost:8000/plot-data/refresh?force=true'
```

## API Endpoints (FastAPI at port 8000)

The backend is FastAPI (not Django). Routes are defined in `backend/app/api/routes/`.

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/health` | GET | Health check |
| `/ib/status` | GET | IB Gateway connection status + accounts |
| `/ib/accounts` | GET | List IB accounts |
| `/ib/accounts/{id}/snapshot` | GET | Account balances + positions |
| `/ib/connect` | POST | Update IB connection host/port at runtime |
| `/portfolios` | GET | List portfolios |
| `/strategies` | GET | List strategies |
| `/allocations` | GET | List allocations |
| `/runs` | GET | List backtest runs |
| `/plot-data` | GET | Get strategy equity curve data |
| `/plot-data/refresh` | POST | Queue Celery task to regenerate plot data |
